Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.14,0:00:03.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From a different perspective...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.92,0:00:05.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An imposing wall is just a large door.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.42,0:00:07.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The stubbord detective, Yokomizo's younger brother
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.09,0:00:09.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the great deduction that amazed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:11.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:12.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:14.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:46.87,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Together with Professor Agassa, we came to collect clams.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:52.80,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}By chance, we met students from the Clam Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:01:58.84,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}However, one of them, Ushigome Tsuguo, died
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.25,0:02:01.55,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}after drinking a poisoned cyanide drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:04.40,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}An examination of the scene
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.44,0:02:06.88,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}showed a high probability of suicide, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:14.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's blood on the neck of the bottle,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.42,0:02:16.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but there's no blood on the lid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.58,0:02:19.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ushigome must have scratched his finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:20.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Scratched it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So when he was picking up the clams,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:25.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he cut himself on a broken shell or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.02,0:02:29.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must have been picking them while he was deep in thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.91,0:02:32.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.45,0:02:36.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed, there's a cut on his index finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:38.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blood clotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.65,0:02:44.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So when he opened the cap the first time, the scratch was still bleeding,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:46.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the blood got on the bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.21,0:02:51.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He brought it here and when he opened it a second time, he noticed the blood on the cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:54.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After wiping off the cap, he opened the bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:09.04,Title,,0,0,0,,CLAM DIGGING WITH A SIGH\N(PART TWO)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:18.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:21.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please don't eat the snacks in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:22.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Want a bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You opened up everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:28.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, how much longer is that younger brother Yokomizo gonna keep us waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:35.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:39.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like an update's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:42.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:46.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:04:00.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, according to the forensics report...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:03.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The substance found inside the green tea was poisonous cyanide derivatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:06.85,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Yashima Mitsue (20)\NCollege Student
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:06.85,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It was also detected from the cap of the plastic bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:12.19,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Mitsuse Takashi (21)\NCollege Student
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:12.19,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Adding to the fact that the jar found in the car also contained the same poison...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:17.90,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hisazu Shouko (21)\NCollege Student
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:16.19,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Looks like we can conclude Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s incident as a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:17.90,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:20.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, whose car is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:23.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a rental car Ushigome paid for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:26.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because he's always the driver whenever we go clam digging.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So do you guys come to this beach often?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:32.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, this is our first time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:35.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We actually planned to come last week, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:38.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Things came up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:40.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we prolonged it until this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:43.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you can fill me in while at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:44.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:48.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did they find any traces of blood on the plastic bottle cap?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:52.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although a minute amount, they did find some.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:54.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Along with Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s fingerprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:55.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Minute amount"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:58.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely when he first unscrewed the cap...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:05:02.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His wound didn't come into much contact with the cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:06.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, now that everything's clear, go home already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:07.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All you kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:08.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:11.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this really a suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:17.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surely Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had opened the plastic bottle lid and started drinking green tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:19.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And nobody else touched it afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:24.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who carried the plastic bottle to this car was also Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:28.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't see any windows of opportunity for anyone to lace the poison...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:31.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's bugging me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:32.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What that person said earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:34.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, why did that person...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:36.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of weird look is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:40.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have a choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:42.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because both my hands are tied!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:45.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why not wrap up your chocolate in that silver foil...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:48.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And put it inside the bag along with the chips?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once I got my hands on the food, I don't want to let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:00.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:01.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you still have the garbage bags with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:05.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:08.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're going to the police station now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:10.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about I throw them away for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:11.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you insist...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:16.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we also drank and ate a lot in the car, so there's quite an amount of trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:20.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are the recyclable plastic bottles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:21.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's the combustible trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:23.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this is non-combustible trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:27.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:29.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:32.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with all those?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:37.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you planning to do, bringing their trash here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:43.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:51.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they had everything sorted out...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:53.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you going to do some crafts?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:55.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you gonna make out of plastic bottles?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:02.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:06.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you're wearing a smug grin on your face...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:08.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you figured out something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:09.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:11.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That it wasn't a suicide at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, who's the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,0:07:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before I reveal that, I have something for you guys to help out with.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:21.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:23.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a little more digging.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:26.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:30.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you already figured out the culprit, why do we have to keep digging like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:36.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention since we're so far away from the water, are we even going to find any clams here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:42.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I recall correctly, this place is where those students had spread out their sheets earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:43.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:48.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To say nothing of clams, even the trash was picked clean and there's absolutely nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:52.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I said, we're not looking for clams, but the plastic bottle...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:58.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:08:00.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found the plastic bottle cap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't touch it, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:06.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It says "green tea" on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:11.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I recall, that guy named Ushigome was also drinking green tea, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:13.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's more, isn't that blood on the lid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:18.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's blackened a little, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:19.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's likely blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:22.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, could it be that cap is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:23.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This should make everything clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:32.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not only the fact that Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} did not commit suicide but was murdered...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:35.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And also the culprit who did this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:39.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we're headed to the station for questioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:41.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So give those three a ride in my car—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:44.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Younger bro, younger bro, younger bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:46.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:50.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:54.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you hear us out first before you take those three to questioning?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:54.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hear you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:56.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because we just figured it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just figured out what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:02.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're telling you—the culprit who killed Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:05.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that culprit was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone who came clam digging with Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:11.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, one of you three!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:25.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, the hell are you yappin' about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:27.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was a suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:33.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was headed to this stationary car in the parking lot all by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:37.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And by the time these three returned from cleaning the trash on the beach...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:40.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He already passed away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:45.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention the green tea bottle laced with poison was lying nearby the vic...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:48.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And next to his feet, we found the same poison jar rolling around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:54.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Based on the testimony that Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was drinking the green tea at the beach just fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:59.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One could only conclude that he mixed poison in his green tea and drank it himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:01.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no other way to look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:03.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But about that green tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:06.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} didn't purchase it himself, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:08.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:11.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was these three people who bought it? but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:16.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yashima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} only handed the plastic green tea bottle to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:19.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuse{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} just tossed him a pack of rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:23.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hisazu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} merely opened up the chips and put it next to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:27.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} unscrewed the green tea lid at the beach...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:30.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,None of those three had touched the plastic bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:35.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was carrying the plastic bottle the entire time, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:39.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So tell me who, when, and how did anyone manage to poison him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:42.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:43.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:48.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's something that always comes with plastic bottles, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:51.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something that comes with plastic bottles would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:57.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The labels that carry the product names?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:01.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, younger bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:03.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cap, the bottle cap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:07.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If one applies poison on the inside of a plastic bottle cap...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:12.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And without touching the plastic bottle, swaps the old cap with this new, poisoned one...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:15.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The poison would be easily mixed in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:18.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, what an amazing deduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:20.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, as much as I want to say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.07,0:11:22.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impracticable, kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:28.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might've worked out if the plastic bottle were still completely filled with green tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:32.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} already opened the screw cap and gulped down a large amount, hadn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:37.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Assuming that's the case, even if the cap was swapped with the poisonous one later...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:41.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The poison on the closed cap wouldn't have reached the green tea at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:46.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, suppose that you apply it on the spiral part inside the cap?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:47.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:51.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, it will go on the mouth of the plastic bottle when he screws the cap back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:56.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's true that his lips will contract poison when he takes a sip that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:11:58.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the toxic substance in question...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:02.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was found in lethal amounts in the green tea contained in the plastic bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:06.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the poison only got on the mouth of the plastic bottle...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:09.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There wouldn't have been much poison in the green tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:11.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if you wanted to mix the poison on the inside of the cap into the green tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:17.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd have to put the plastic bottle upside down or...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:20.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shake the bottle with a splashing sound for it to get mixed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:24.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} have a habit like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:25.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:28.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'd shake it only if it's tomato juice or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:29.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps he laid it {\i1}sideways{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:31.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sideways?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:33.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I recall, Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:36.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Returned to the car while carrying two buckets, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:40.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:44.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How come Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had to carry the buckets himself and none of you helped out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:48.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because Ushigome was the one who knew the most about clams.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:53.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he's always in charge of picking up the clams and cleaning the sand out of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:56.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although we were the ones who had to cook it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:12:59.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it always two buckets?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:01.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, about right
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:04.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't care about that trivial stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:08.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm asking you to answer why you said "sideways"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:09.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:13.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had to hold the two buckets and both of his hands were occupied!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:15.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm asking...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:20.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, he'd either have to put the plastic bottle in the bucket, under his arms...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:22.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or inside the kangaroo pocket of his hoodie like the ones you're wearing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Placing it sideways, wouldn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:34.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} did keep the plastic bottle sideways inside his pocket like that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:37.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:40.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it were sideways, the green tea inside would shake whenever he walks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:44.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This trick guarantees that by the time he reached the parking lot, the poison on the inside of the cap...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:47.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would have been completely mixed into the green tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:50.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:51.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, still...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:56.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if he didn't conveniently happen to put on a hoodie with a pocket like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:13:59.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he didn't just "happen to" wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:05.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What these people are wearing is the matching hoodies they made for their Clam Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:11.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And since it was made not long ago, if someone suggested that they wear it for today's clam digging...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:13.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} also comply and wear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:19.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus, since Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had always carried two buckets and returned to the car before you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:26.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone could have easily predicted that he would put the plastic bottle in his hoodie pocket sideways.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:29.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to agree it's possible to mix poison that way, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:34.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The problem is, who was able to swap the poisonous cap and how?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:38.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Normally, when you unscrew a cap, you would likely put it near you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:47.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had also placed it somewhere on the sheet he was sitting on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:51.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, since all that Yashima lady did...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:55.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was hand him the plastic bottle...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:58.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for her to have swapped it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:02.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And still, that Mitsuse mister...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:06.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did nothing other than tossing him the pack of rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:12.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if he were to stretch his arm and attempt to switch the cap sitting on the sheet, he would've been seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:17.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, that leaves us with the person who placed the bag of chips next to Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:19.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hisazu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:23.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apparently you had the best chance to swap out the cap sitting on the sheet
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.31,0:15:25.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:29.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on, what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:31.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could she if all she did was to put down a bag of chips?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:35.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That bag of chips is the perfect camouflage for the deed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:43.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hisazu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} placed the bag of chips immediately next to Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:47.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You simply had to hold the poisoned cap between your fingers beforehand...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:49.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And swapped the caps with the bag obstructing the view.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:53.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Having done so, Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} would mistake the cap as the one he put
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:58.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So how come there's blood on the mouth of the plastic bottle and none on the cap?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:03.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The answer is because the vic touched the swapped poisonous cap after his finger wound began to heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:10.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, even if his wound was closing, he still used the same finger to unscrew and screw the cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:13.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why we detected a minute amount of blood even on the poisonous cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:15.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that how it played out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:18.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:20.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:25.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means the original cap with Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s blood should be around somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:28.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you guys have some bags of trash?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We gave them to the brat with glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:34.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:36.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you've examined the caps?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:40.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But even though there were six plastic bottles...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:41.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only found five caps.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:45.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only the cap of the empty green tea bottle was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:47.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So is this what transpired?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:53.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First she had Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} drink up a whole bottle of green tea that she bought in advance...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:55.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And filched the cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:17:00.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then she laced poison on it somewhere else, and replaced the newly bought green tea bottle cap with it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:05.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, all she had to do is to suggest going home at the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:09.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} would return to the car and likely drink up the remaining poisoned tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:15.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later on, if the police discovered the jar with toxicant she had left in the car beforehand...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:17.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would make it ostensibly a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:19.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps that jar was also...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:25.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Swiped from Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} without his permission in order to use it as a staged suicide prop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:29.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, your calculations were thrown off when you were swapping the caps.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:36.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cap had already been smeared in Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:39.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you didn't throw it in the trash bag, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:44.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we had collected that, we would have figured out it was swapped out
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:49.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although you may have already tossed away that bloody cap somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:50.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We could always try searching the beach where you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:52.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already thought of that and found it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:54.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:57.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The green tea bottle cap with blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:13.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, how could that be proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:17.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're talking about fingerprints, she had already touched it during the convenience store purchase!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.11,0:18:19.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,-Nah, I'm not talking about fingerprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:23.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By coming into contact with the cap...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:26.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hisazu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s fingers would likely test positive for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:29.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The evidence that you touched Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:32.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A luminol reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:35.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, Shouko, are you all right with him accusing you all he wants?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you retort him!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:39.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell him he can search all he wants and get nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:42.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't retort him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:46.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because what that officer just said...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:47.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every bit of it was the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:50.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't tell me it's because of that accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:51.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:54.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:55.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:56.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, do you recall?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:18:59.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hit-and-run incident here last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:02.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it has something to do with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:06.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since they showed a gloomy look, when that topic was brought up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hit-and-run?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:10.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one that involved hitting a drunkard?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:13.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that was you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:15.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we didn't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not until we saw the newspaper the next day!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:17.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:18.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:19.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:20.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:23.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:26.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} said we might have hit something...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:30.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We all got out of the car and checked around immediately, but didn't see anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:31.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:34.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was someone at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:39.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the patch of grass where I checked...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:42.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A man was lying on the ground, drenched in blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:44.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why didn't you say anything!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:45.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:48.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man wasn't breathing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:49.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} had been drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:53.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we were found out, we'd lose our new jobs that are so hard to come by!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:55.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:58.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If only Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} would've kept his mouth shut...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:20:00.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he didn't start talking about turning himself in...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.88,0:20:04.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're just like a clam.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:07.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how well you think you've hidden...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:10.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll always leave behind a trace somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:15.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That troublesome something will become more apparent the more you try to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:19.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} didn't own up, we police would've still tracked you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:24.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By sniffing out that rotten hole in your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:07.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've finally cleaned these all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:10.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't just leave them here after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.39,0:22:16.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But to think that you ascertained the culprit's identity just by seeing the bag of chips placed next to victim...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.39,0:22:19.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not the only thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.11,0:22:22.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I mentioned the mouth of the plastic bottle had blood on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.57,0:22:27.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She blurted out that Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} injured his finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.61,0:22:30.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.99,0:22:34.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just happened to know that he had cut his finger, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.58,0:22:37.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Normally if there's blood on the mouth of a plastic bottle...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.66,0:22:42.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't people assume that it was either because his lips cracked, or there's a wound in his mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.09,0:22:47.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially since there was no blood on the cap found next to Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.84,0:22:49.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how I figured out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:55.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason why Hisazu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said that was because she saw the cap with blood when she did the switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:01.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it just like you said, Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.19,0:23:05.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.57,0:23:07.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:09.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll need you to come to the station later as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.65,0:23:11.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bring the brats too...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.16,0:23:13.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some of the brats are gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.74,0:23:15.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.58,0:23:16.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.37,0:23:18.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're looking for them...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.54,0:23:21.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They went back to the beach in a big rush just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:23.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saying they lost some very important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:26.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.84,0:23:29.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it was a Yaiba figure we had never seen before!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.13,0:23:32.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, and you really don't remember where you dropped it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:35.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I did, I would've found it by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.39,0:23:38.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was super rare!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.81,0:23:41.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the kind we'll never get if we don't buy a truckload.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.23,0:23:45.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys love it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:23:45.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Digging in the sand...
